snippet.title: Resident Evil 7 biohazard Gold Edition: TAPE-02 “Redfield”
snippet.description:
Chris Redfield returns, and Zoe Baker’s fate is revisited in this new video for Not a Hero and End of Zoe, both out Dec. 12th alongside Resident Evil 7 biohazard Gold Edition for PS4, Xbox One, and PC.
